<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201104/7c38f1a29c8a43f1b3139c21d09efde7.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201104/8d75492b2bba4417abbeb76b01f66740.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>过去的6年里，</p>
<p>一条挖掘、报道了成百上千位独具匠心的手作职人，</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
